<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>FEATURES</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/navatyle.css">
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <%- include('header.ejs') %>

   <div class="features">
      <h2>Features</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card image_box">
          <img
            src="/public/images/treatment planning.gif"
            class="card-img-top box"
            alt="..."
          />

          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Treatment Planning</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              AI models can be trained on vast datasets of patient information
              and outcomes to suggest personalized treatment plans tailored to
              individual needs. This can optimize treatment strategies and
              potentially improve patient recovery.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card image_box">
          <img
            src="/public/images/diagonosis and assesment .gif"
            class="card-img-top box"
            alt="..."
          />

          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Diagonsis & Assesment</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              AI algorithms can analyze medical images, such as photographs of
              burns, to accurately assess burn depth, size, and even predict
              potential complications. This can assist healthcare professionals
              in making quicker and more informed decisions about treatment
              approaches
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card image_box">
          <img src="/public/images/skin.gif" class="card-img-top box" alt="..." />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Fluid Resuscitation</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              AI can analyze patient data and physiological parameters to guide
              fluid resuscitation, a crucial element of burn care that requires
              precise management to prevent complications like fluid overload.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4 mt-3">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card image_box">
          <img src="/public/images/modelling.gif" class="card-img-top box" alt="..." />

          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Predictive Modelling</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              AI can be used to develop models that predict the risk of
              developing specific complications after a burn, such as sepsis or
              pneumonia. This allows healthcare professionals to take proactive
              measures to prevent these complications and improve overall
              patient outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card image_box">
          <img src="/public/images/faq.gif" class="card-img-top box" alt="..." />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">FAQ</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Here you will find concise answers to commonly asked questions.
              Whether you're seeking information on our product, services, or
              policies, we're here to provide clarity and support.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card image_box">
          <img src="/public/images/consultation.gif" class="card-img-top box" alt="..." />
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Online Consultation</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Discover convinience with our online consultation services.
              Receive expert advice and guidance from the comfort of your home.
              Book appointments, ask questions, and get personalized
              recommendations hassle-free.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    
     <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>
